msgid "Frontliner"
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Frontliner, race=eoma_tharis
#: Era_of_Magic\units\Tharis\Frontliner.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Frontliners are a special caste of warriors distinguished by their "
"preference for brutal, upfront combat. Unlike their fellow Tharis soldiers, "
"who rely on stealth and subterfuge to gain the upper hand, Frontliners "
"charge into battle with reckless abandon, relying on their superior strength "
"and weaponry to obliterate any opposition. Equipped with dual curved swords "
"crafted for maximum bloodletting, these warriors specialize in disabling "
"their enemies with swift, decisive blows, leaving them vulnerable to "
"subsequent attacks from behind. By clearing the path ahead of the main "
"offensive force, Frontliners enable their comrades to advance with relative "
"ease, making them indispensable in any military campaign."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Great_Hunter, race=eoma_tharis
#: Era_of_Magic\units\Tharis\Great_Hunter.cfg:4
msgid "Great Hunter"
msgstr "高级暗黑猎人"

#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Great_Hunter, race=eoma_tharis
#: Era_of_Magic\units\Tharis\Great_Hunter.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The elite among Dark Hunters, those who have proven themselves superior to "
"their peers, are elevated to the rank of Great Hunter. These exceptional "
"warriors move with fluid grace, their blades flashing silver in the light of "
"the full moon as they strike with deadly precision. But when it comes to "
"capturing their prey, Great Hunters don't rely on crude traps or brute "
"force. Instead, they employ sophisticated nets crafted from rare, silky "
"threads that can ensnare even the most cunning of quarry."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Raging_Hydra, race=monster
#: Era_of_Magic\units\Tharis\Great_Hydra.cfg:4
msgid "Great Hydra"
msgstr "巨型九头蛇"

#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Raging_Hydra, race=monster
#: Era_of_Magic\units\Tharis\Great_Hydra.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Risen from the depths of the underground tunnels like a nightmarish "
"manifestation, this towering, mature Great Hydra brooks no opposition. Its "
"sheer size and ferocity make it a terror beyond compare, with three twisted "
"heads, each one seemingly more malevolent than the last, the beast stalks "
"its prey with unrelenting determination, leaving a trail of destruction in "
"its wake. Those who have witnessed this abomination up close live only to "
"bear witness to its fury, their screams and pleas for mercy lost to the "
"echoes of the caverns."
msgstr ""

#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Great_Warlock, race=eoma_tharis
#: Era_of_Magic\units\Tharis\Great_Warlock.cfg:4
msgid "Great Warlock"
msgstr "暗黑术士"

#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Great_Warlock, race=eoma_tharis
#: Era_of_Magic\units\Tharis\Great_Warlock.cfg:21
msgid ""
"To become a Great Warlock, the pinnacle of achievement for any Tharis mage, "
"is a lifelong pursuit of mastery over the dark arts. These powerful "
"practitioners possess unparalleled skill in black magic, able to wield it "
"with precision and deadliness. The secret of levitation has been fully "
"realized by Great Warlocks, enabling them to traverse vast distances with "
"ease, even across treacherous terrain. As a symbol of their status and "
"prowess, they carry ceremonial scythes, imbued with the power of the dark "
"arts and used to devastating effect in battle. But it is not merely brute "
"strength that distinguishes Great Warlocks; they are also accomplished "
"strategists and tacticians. They can weave complex spell combinations, "
"exploiting weaknesses in enemy defenses and catching them off guard. With "
"each victory, their mastery grows, and their reputation spreads like "
"wildfire throughout the realm."
msgstr ""

